article_title: How Brandon Cruz of GoHealth shares success

article_metadata.description: GoHealth president and co-founder Brandon Cruz leads an online health insurance marketplace that enrolled people in Obamacare and is growing its mobile presence quickly. He shares his thoughts on team-building.
